[src:module-theory/tensor-product-of-modules] To give a practical example, suppose *M*, *N* are free modules with bases $e_{i},i\in I$ and $f_{j},j\in J$ .
[src:module-theory/tensor-product-of-modules] Then *M* is the direct sum $M=\bigoplus _{i\in I}Re_{i}$ and the same for *N*.
