[src:module-theory/tensor-product-of-modules] Thus, $\mathbb {C} \otimes _{\mathbb {R} }\mathbb {C}$ and $\mathbb {C} \otimes _{\mathbb {C} }\mathbb {C}$ are not isomorphic.
